{{!
    @template mod_booking/form_booking_instances_selector_suggestion

    Moodle template for a booking instance suggestion in an autocomplete form element.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * id int booking instance id
    * text string name of the booking instance
    * coursename string name of the course

    Example context (json):
    {
        "id": 1,
        "text": "My Booking Instance",
        "coursename": "Course 101"
    }
}}
<span>
    <span class="booking-instance-suggestion font-weight-bold">{{text}}<small> ID: {{id}}</small></span>
    <div><small>{{coursename}}</small></div>
</span>
